</div><div class="center_content">
  <div class="news_post"> Hello and welcome to Reality Dynasty's Clan Management System. General and higher are granted access so that they can maintain a list of the members in their squads. This is done so that we have the information even if we lose a squad tag for some reason. This also lets our leaders be able to know in a glance which areas of RD are doing help, and which ones may need assistance. You are expected to update your squad list at least 2-3 times a week to ensure that we always have accurate information. If you have any issues, please go to our forums and post a topic in the "Site Errors" section and your problem will be dealt with as soon as possible.   </div>
